{"tid":989253,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實Twice真係進步咗好多㗎","createTime":"2019-01-20T16:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T10:20:11.000Z","uid":217593,"like":20,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8d49cde75192601bad313cdbc07e0206b21379bb","tid":989253,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"佢地咪嘴就眾所皆知㗎啦，但前日Music Bank in HK唔知係咪想話比大家知佢地出咗道咁耐並唔係原地踏步，無進步，佢地竟然好大膽咁開咪唱live！<br />\n<br />\n有生之年聽到佢地唱live真係三生有幸！成晚四首歌大山婆走咗三次音，唔記得邊首歌，多腎rap都廢事，做翻老本行繼續咪嘴。其實根據翻佢地實力，出咗道差唔多五年都算係咁啦，由原本唔敢唱live，到沉日鼓起勇氣，就算知自己實力未如理想，都要唱live俾大家聽，話俾大家知佢地係實力派Idol<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實Twice會唔會考慮下繼續咪嘴，唔好虐待大眾嘅耳朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd84cc3a192b1435d32f584712e22a98dd1a0b78","tid":989253,"uid":52073,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"TWICE勁係人都知架啦 4代入面都冇邊幾隊夠佢地打"},{"pid":"886175cfbaf9bfbee73d227a385cf95591982586","tid":989253,"uid":217593,"like":23,"dislike":12,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"bd84cc3a192b1435d32f584712e22a98dd1a0b78","tid":989253,"uid":52073,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"TWICE勁係人都知架啦 4代入面都冇邊幾隊夠佢地打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"平心而論，佢地實力係四代入面真係差，只係公司不停迫佢地係咁回歸唱埋啲口水歌洗人腦，同埋隊入面有三個架妹俾班毒撚j先咁紅"},{"pid":"df7d33b33fe11604c099fa238deb6693ced113b8","tid":989253,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"有無link"},{"pid":"741f5251f69c92d3b8986559e531269ffb606f14","tid":989253,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:30:06.000Z","msg":"MOMO D唱功進步得好犀利"},{"pid":"34133dbf87a17ceaa7e71cfc26ff13497a38d84e","tid":989253,"uid":143375,"like":1,"di